short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Transfer the currently opened URL into your Cluefeed.com bookmark archive.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Cluefeed.com is a social know-how aggregator: Collect your bookmarks, access them from any device on the go, share them, and get recommendations based on your interests.

With this Google Chrome Extension, you can easily add the currently opened page to your Clufeed Bookmark Archive.
